==Discography==
===Roles Turned Down===
According to Hunter, he turned down the following roles:
* the lead in &quot;Darby&#x27;s Rangers&quot;
* the lead in &quot;Bombers B-52&quot;
* replacing Paul Newman on Broadway in &quot;Sweet Bird of Youth&quot;
